{"tid":1744805,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[當抗爭變成工作][有圖]黃絲經濟圈之進化永動機","createTime":"2019-11-22T02:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T07:15:31.000Z","uid":305022,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1e2280fb3b1d31edd666de74894a70d5f56b9dbc","tid":1744805,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:20:36.000Z","msg":"「我要返工」良心平台 Channel<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680524</a><br />\n<br />\n好多謝有心人開左呢個平台比各位手足返工，但係好多時候返工都要一定既經驗同學歷或者技能先會有人請，為左照顧各個唔同階層年紀既手足，點解我地唔張一啲有用，簡單，既抗爭活動作為工作內容呢？<br />\n。<br />\n小弟閒餘幫手貼下牆派下傳單，攪放映會甚至係傾計booth。由於我呢排越黎越忙，無辦法做到親力親為，我決定張以上呢幾樣野工作化，透過呢個平台申請做僱主，並且出兼職人工比做呢啲野既手足，例如：<br />\n<br />\n1. 派文宣傳單段鐘計／段張數計<br />\n2. 放映會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個要預備物資比較多，未必適合想彈性番既手足<br />\n3. TG booth 同上，但只需要一張枱同埋少量文宣<br />\n以上3樣應該唔會比狗攪，相對安全<br />\n<br />\n希望各位手足特別係被捕左，呢排要低調轉和理非既都搵到外快支持落去。<br />\n<br />\n黃絲比錢請手足做文宣地區工作--&gt;手足有飯開---&gt; 地區工作突破同溫層---&gt;增加黃絲數量---&gt;增加金錢支援---&gt;更多手足有飯開<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下為之前做過既相。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4sHVbTT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4sHVbTT.jpg&h=6d5e805f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但小弟一個人心力財力有限，希望各位金主有能力既做多啲，唔一定要係現任公司或者老闆先至幫到手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83b95aa3e797a8cd0d7e41b1f64c3b54a578b89","tid":1744805,"uid":10274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ujihqjG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FujihqjG.jpg&h=a3acda04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"355927503042ef09f4ab495d73ba60d6a6f24cf9","tid":1744805,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:45:23.000Z","msg":"回應阿正<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b316d7ab4cf9a6735b3d729ffca3cebc97590df4","tid":1744805,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:50:56.000Z","msg":"Ｐ牌ＰＯＳＴ無人覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e22535c52c23c9bc987cfb6de1eb85bf73777e","tid":1744805,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:53:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89123ed626c0c2a2330a2431ad128dc533a92bed","tid":1744805,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:19:00.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"958c04bce3454f27c41c04bc800b16ef309cc109","tid":1744805,"uid":44046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:23:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d77e0467a29ff70bff4147c84e52995c207b06ee","tid":1744805,"uid":33303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:23:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a00ca32de8942ea5b11796dd12b426183b4c7c10","tid":1744805,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:32:05.000Z","msg":"Ｐ牌POST 推唔郁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c235562c33b9c78405eac375dec48bab49f08893","tid":1744805,"uid":16792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:05:55.000Z